[Aug 15]
English High School AC 5:0 Quilmes
   [S. Leonard, H. Jordan, W. A. Jordan, J. Moore, S. Leonard]
   
English High School Athletic Club won the championship in this round with the 
following line-ups:

English High School AC:    J. McKechnie; Jorge Gibson Brown, Walter Buchanan; 
                           Andrés Arturo Mack (c), Carlos Buchanan, Ernesto 
                           Brown; H. Jordan, Eugenio Moore, S. Leonard, Juan J. 
                           Moore, W. A. Jordan
Quilmes:                   Ernst Cunningham; William Leslie, F. Parry; Ronald 
                           Muir, J. H. Williams, W. Dunne; C. Comber, H. Torre, 
                           P. Hooton, E. O. Morgan, William Stirling.
Referee:                   Barrington Blomfield Syer.

